{"tid":2312684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好無力？唔知做咩好？","createTime":"2020-12-05T07:21:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T13:16:47.000Z","uid":229502,"like":31,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"c7ebc7c13596dfee267c8ac9080c4865315027cd","tid":2312684,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:21:05.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"orange\">TLDR:呢排好辛苦，但我哋要做嘅唔係抱怨現況，而係諗喺現況可以做啲咩，諗到做咩就去做，覺得攰就抖，抖完再返返嚟</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n見到呢排咁多負面消息，美國大選都冇咩新轉機，打壓愈嚟愈嚴重好辛苦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我哋要做嘅唔係抱怨現況，而係諗喺現況可以做啲咩<br />\n<br />\n12港人被囚禁超過百日，聽聞就嚟開庭，我哋實際冇咩可以做到係直接幫佢哋，但其實我哋有好多嘢<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">Twitter、Reddit線</span> （就算奶共/直接受中共操縱都好，但擺脫唔到全世界仲有好多人用嘅事實）<br />\n<br />\n叫人轉Mewe，但唔好完全唔用Facebook，因仲有好多人用，嗰啲話轉唔到嘅，當年Myspace轉Facebook都係咁轉啦，點解依家唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">TVB(/有線)戰線</span>，依家情況又衰返，可唔可以幫下手？你可能覺得我語氣好差，但呢樣嘢係得你先做到，你唔做，其他人都唔會跟住做<br />\n<br />\n其實依家先係關鍵時刻，唔想成日瞓喺張床度，咁咪做下運動，出唔到街咪拉下筋或者做體能，好過喺度怨天尤人<br />\n<br />\n如果出到街，咁咪喺<span class=\"red\"><strong>安全同冇CCTV</strong></span>嘅時候貼文宣，幫襯黃店，呢個時勢唔止藍店，好多黃店都頂唔住<br />\n<br />\n我都係成日好擔心，但係淨係擔心冇用㗎，乜嘢都唔會改變，由最近嘅地方開始做起，最後一定會有改變，要記住你唔係一個人，攰咗可以抖，但抖完我哋隨時歡迎你返嚟。<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多好多嘢可以做，我哋一齊加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4c5f659ff4372ffcacd70164b96e6379825c307","tid":2312684,"uid":142002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:21:54.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7629c5f8f54a7ca40e41f26f1b56aae8a3e76b7","tid":2312684,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:22:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e67672227ae20b829a74743e5c958c26e0a2d689","tid":2312684,"uid":142002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:22:09.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b75ee89cd334112cc7246e9bbd16cb625fdcbe7","tid":2312684,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:22:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f4f9840c2d880de727fabd661bec33bb1d3ec8","tid":2312684,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:22:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f39d49169b5a381b0c4a3ef7375d782dfc6ef5a1","tid":2312684,"uid":142002,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:22:46.000Z","msg":"Upup<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6284fb13dacd8086d842f1d636def011e5be52e1","tid":2312684,"uid":142002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:23:12.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3c8dae95b6d0abc6f3413a4a6924d90e2584aa7","tid":2312684,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:23:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e37c7e565f544337110392b6082fa5bbed2a546","tid":2312684,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:23:33.