=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"195b15fcfd67d4e892efc529d6da7a7b4e525b47","tid":2312684,"uid":251009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:42:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"825cf9be2883aa3f2e4eb880899bd67d9667a8c0","tid":2312684,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:42:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8253bc5d4711ceb1a166a5c43063e95496df3168","tid":2312684,"uid":251009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:42:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5b8745361c5085b302d676a5c9461cbbba7ca3f","tid":2312684,"uid":124087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3067aa022abdd1a7dba913d2b612ee97ea91ad76","tid":2312684,"uid":356542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c7ebc7c13596dfee267c8ac9080c4865315027cd","tid":2312684,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:21:05.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"orange\">TLDR:呢排好辛苦，但我哋要做嘅唔係抱怨現況，而係諗喺現況可以做啲咩，諗到做咩就去做，覺得攰就抖，抖完再返返嚟</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n見到呢排咁多負面消息，美國大選都冇咩新轉機，打壓愈嚟愈嚴重好辛苦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我哋要做嘅唔係抱怨現況，而係諗喺現況可以做啲咩<br />\n<br />\n12港人被囚禁超過百日，聽聞就嚟開庭，我哋實際冇咩可以做到係直接幫佢哋，但其實我哋有好多嘢<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">Twitter、Reddit線</span> （就算奶共/直接受中共操縱都好，但擺脫唔到全世界仲有好多人用嘅事實）<br />\n<br />\n叫人轉Mewe，但唔好完全唔用Facebook，因仲有好多人用，嗰啲話轉唔到嘅，當年Myspace轉Facebook都係咁轉啦，點解依家唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">TVB(/有線)戰線</span>，依家情況又衰返，可唔可以幫下手？你可能覺得我語氣好差，但呢樣嘢係得你先做到，你唔做，其他人都唔會跟住做<br />\n<br />\n其實依家先係關鍵時刻，唔想成日瞓喺張床度，咁咪做下運動，出唔到街咪拉下筋或者做體能，好過喺度怨天尤人<br />\n<br />\n如果出到街，咁咪喺<span class=\"red\"><strong>安全同冇CCTV</strong></span>嘅時候貼文宣，幫襯黃店，呢個時勢唔止藍店，好多黃店都頂唔住<br />\n<br />\n我都係成日好擔心，但係淨係擔心冇用㗎，乜嘢都唔會改變，由最近嘅地方開始做起，最後一定會有改變，要記住你唔係一個人，攰咗可以抖，但抖完我哋隨時歡迎你返嚟。<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多好多嘢可以做，我哋一齊加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:27:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:42:32.000Z","msg":"系"},{"pid":"bedffbbd473dfeeed0d8884067ba964c604a8353","tid":2312684,"uid":251009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:42:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30247b91d4ba4ee503478a326c3d06a49683d0d3","tid":2312684,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:43:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f0b98c4228dc4372ba8fdbde1ba901a3e15a5ac","tid":2312684,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c3677f7cfffe9991da1f6dfcf170520475ee702","tid":2312684,"uid":251009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccf9c5f2557ff81088396f76ce9f263dab2abeee","tid":2312684,"uid":166308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97fd96025ae471f1711f1575a1da2c1346bc77fe","tid":2312684,"uid":229502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:32:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T07:32:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 